# ==============================================================================
# Quality Profiles
# ==============================================================================
profile.VERY_LOW=Napakababa
profile.VERY_LOW.comment=Fastest possible preset for very weak GPUs. Disables shadows, clouds, water waves, foliage waving, PBR and most extras.
profile.LOW=Mababa
profile.LOW.comment=Lightweight preset for weak GPUs. Keeps cheap water/foliage motion, disables shadows, clouds and PBR.
profile.MED=Katamtaman
profile.MED.comment=Balanced preset with 1024 shadows, standard clouds, PBR and atmospheric effects.
profile.HIGH=Mataas
profile.HIGH.comment=High quality preset with 2048 shadows, farther clouds and full PBR, without SSAO.
profile.ULTRA=Ultra
profile.ULTRA.comment=Ultra quality preset with 4096 shadows, very far clouds and balanced SSAO. POM remains disabled for stability.
profile.EXTREME=Sukdulan
profile.EXTREME.comment=Maximum experimental quality. Pushes lighting, clouds, color and deep SSAO. POM remains disabled for stability.
profile.CUSTOM=Custom
profile.CUSTOM.comment=Custom na mga setting na binago ng user.

screen.TRANSLATION_NOTICE=⚠ Maaaring may mali sa mga salin
screen.TRANSLATION_NOTICE.comment=Maaaring hindi tumpak ang ilang mga string ng lokalisasyon. Kung may mukhang kakaiba, ihambing sa orihinal na Ingles.

# Screens
screen.LIGHTING=Mga Setting ng Ilaw
screen.LIGHTING.comment=I-configure ang mga anino, kulay ng ilaw, at liwanag.

screen.FOLIAGE=Mga Setting ng Halaman
screen.FOLIAGE.comment=I-configure ang mga animation ng pag-alon para sa damo at dahon.

screen.WATER=Mga Setting ng Tubig
screen.WATER.comment=I-configure ang mga alon, transparency, at estilo ng tubig.

screen.CLOUDS_MENU=Langit at Ulap
screen.CLOUDS_MENU.comment=I-configure ang pisikal na taas, kapal, at estilo ng 3D na ulap at mga epekto ng langit.

screen.POST_PROCESS=Post-Processing at Hamog
screen.POST_PROCESS.comment=I-configure ang exposure, ulap, at sineng epekto.

